{"tid":622764,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[LIHKG]動漫台緣份計劃意見及人口調查　","createTime":"2018-04-09T11:50:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-09T15:55:35.000Z","uid":34293,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"061566c6eb1bb28a2b066df744095c6812f296e2","tid":622764,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T11:50:48.000Z","msg":"<del>在動漫台尋求邂逅是否搞錯了什麼?</del><br />\n<br />\n大家好，小弟有意係LIHKG搞只屬於動漫台既緣份計劃，比大家認識興趣相近既異性或同性啦。<br />\n想大家花小小時間填份問卷比意見，睇下可唔可行，多唔多人參與。如果過半數反對我自己收皮。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外，仲想做個人口調查，統計大家瀏覽動漫台既習慣。個人對動漫台既生態圈好有興趣，希望兩星期內整到個報告比大家。<br />\n歡迎大家提出唔同既意見<del>/狠評</del>，感謝各位。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n問卷調查Link:<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/forms/e6Plh03iiQCCX5p73\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fforms%2Fe6Plh03iiQCCX5p73&d=VPqP6xKM9lOwx49ngsWX2DPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=1a5d52b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/forms/e6Plh03iiQCCX5p73</a><br />\n<br />\nReference: <br />\n好宅之人 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/veryotaku\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fveryotaku&d=VPqP6xKM9lOwx49ngsWX2DPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=3e3e7f9c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/veryotaku</a><br />\n緣份配對計劃 <a href=\"https://matchup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmatchup.hk&d=VPqP6xKM9lOwx49ngsWX2DPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=423e0100\" target=\"_blank\">https://matchup.hk</a>"},{"pid":"9605499ce746a32300abf287adb1c0808c8c9500","tid":622764,"uid":606,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T11:56:56.000Z","msg":"男同男嘅緣份有咩好調查"},{"pid":"a598b4cbd9737dbef0c87090e0a050000b81f7a2","tid":622764,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9605499ce746a32300abf287adb1c0808c8c9500","tid":622764,"uid":606,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T11:56:56.000Z","msg":